flowchart LR
  Web["Web / API client"] --> ApiRoute["API Gateway<br/>POST /api/v1/recommendations"]
  ApiRoute --> AgentLambda["Lambda: lovv-dev-api-AgentCoreFunction-*<br/>현재 env는 V1 runtime ARN"]

  AgentLambda --> V1["Bedrock AgentCore<br/>LovvAgentCore_LovvAgentV1<br/>READY, version 13"]
  AgentLambda -. "V2 전환 대상" .-> V2["Bedrock AgentCore<br/>LovvAgentCore_LovvAgentV2<br/>READY, version 1"]

  V1 --> AgentGraph["Agent graph<br/>intent / destination / itinerary / scoring"]
  V2 --> AgentGraph

  AgentGraph --> Vector["S3 Vector<br/>lovv-vector-dev / kr-tour-domain-v2"]
  AgentGraph --> DomainDDB["DynamoDB<br/>TourKoreaDomainDataV2"]
  AgentGraph --> Profile["DynamoDB<br/>LovvAgentCore-LovvUserProfile<br/>0 items"]
  AgentGraph --> Events["DynamoDB<br/>lovv_dev_user_event_logs<br/>0 items"]
  AgentGraph --> Runs["DynamoDB<br/>lovv_dev_agent_runs<br/>0 items"]
  AgentGraph --> SavedPlans["Aurora MySQL<br/>itineraries / itinerary_items / plan_reactions"]

  Vector --> Hydrate["ddb_pk / ddb_sk로 DynamoDB hydrate"]
  DomainDDB --> Hydrate
  Profile -. "개인화 입력 부족" .-> AgentGraph
  Events -. "행동 로그 없음" .-> AgentGraph
  SavedPlans -. "저장 일정 기반 프로파일 연결 확인 필요" .-> AgentGraph

  AgentGraph --> Response["추천 일정 / 후보지 / 설명 응답"]
  Response --> AgentLambda
  AgentLambda --> ApiRoute
